Neutron flux ~10**13 n/cm2 during irradiation of ~8hr.
The effective flux was determined from induced beta
activity of Zr and Al samples.
two by relative method - 250+-100 mb, 270 +- 90 mb;
two by absolute method - 270+-110 mb, 240 +-110 mb.
Correction for fluctuation of neutron flux was
determined by numerical integration and was < 0.8 %.
